254
00:20:43,160 --> 00:20:44,832
Parker Posey.
Ander terrein.

255
00:20:49,625 --> 00:20:51,012
Wil jij met me...

256
00:20:57,132 --> 00:20:58,425
Motor één is uitgevallen.

